{"tid":729291,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Ahhhhhhhhh...買咗張JR West Rail Pass，有一日free day去邊好？","createTime":"2018-07-04T12:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T14:46:50.000Z","uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"abf16e6fb730f49090a0068f92e4db39eec99df5","tid":729291,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"本身諗用plan個日係去usj，但係又想用盡張pass，<br />\n咁啱大阪市內都無乜興趣行(本身留多一日行大阪)，就決定提前去usj，<br />\n咁就突咗一日出嚟唔知做乜好，求提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經行過京都嵐山奈良，之後會去神戶姬路（同一日），仲有會去白濱同和歌山（呢排關西開始狂落雨，仲想行熊野古道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），<br />\n有諗過覆桌京都，因為未去鴨川就過咗嚟大阪，或者神戶姬路分兩日去，甚至有諗過去岡山即日來回，<br />\n前提係大阪來回，所以想問吓意見再決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60148d35be11ddb6f2bc7d28d84ce78d34874044","tid":729291,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"打漏係5日 關西廣域卷，成日搞亂啲名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0bd08591d3dff3fc90bb96e440fc4d8ad09ed8","tid":729291,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"入熊野都要預一個full day啦？"},{"pid":"a59ed904b27f21bd991e89f9d7011061ab2088cc","tid":729291,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f0bd08591d3dff3fc90bb96e440fc4d8ad09ed8","tid":729291,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"入熊野都要預一個full day啦？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"預咗，5日day pass本身係咁用<br />\nD1 大阪即日來回姬路神戶<br />\nD2 usj<br />\nD3 大阪直去白濱 （唔行和歌山）<br />\nD4 熊野古道 （有時間就去埋那智瀑布）<br />\nD5 白濱直去關西機場上夜機"},{"pid":"c7691e8341373728fed593a07ffac1d8ec528c13",